                                        <span class="text-sm text-gray-400">Jul 2, 2025</span>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="flex text-yellow-500 text-[0.7rem]  mb-2">
                                        <i class="fas fa-star mr-[1px]"></i>
                                        <i class="fas fa-star mr-[1px]"></i>
                                        <i class="fas fa-star mr-[1px]"></i>
                                        <i class="fas fa-star mr-[1px]"></i>
                                        <i class="fas fa-star-half-alt"></i>
                                    </div>
                                    <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Great quality sunglasses, fits perfectly and looks
